## DASHBOARD Quick Reference (Section 10 of DESIGN_BRIEF.md)

**Use ONLY this section for `/dashboard/*` and all authenticated pages. Ignore landing rules above.**

### Vibe (3 reference screenshots)
- **Nixtio dashboard:** light cool-white bg `#F0F4FF`, white cards, electric blue + mint green charts
- **Getillustrations:** mint `#2ECC88` + black outlines for illustrations and illustration-style accents
- **Playground/Emote:** ultra-bold black Inter headlines, pastel card bgs, `rounded-2xl` cards

### Dashboard Fonts
- **ONE font only:** Inter (no Lora ever)
- **KPI numbers:** `text-[36px] font-extrabold tracking-tight text-gray-900` — heavy and punchy
- **Page title:** `text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-gray-900`
- **Card title:** `text-[15px] font-semibold text-gray-900`
- **Body / labels:** `text-sm text-gray-600` or `text-xs text-gray-400`

### Dashboard Colors
- **Page bg:** `bg-[#F0F4FF]` — light cool blue-white (NOT dark, NOT gray)
- **Card bg:** `bg-white` — pure white
- **Primary accent:** `bg-[#2ECC88]` mint/emerald green — CTAs, recovered amounts, success
- **Secondary accent:** `bg-[#4361EE]` electric blue — active nav, links, charts series 2
- **Text primary:** `text-gray-900` (`#111827`) — KPIs, headings
- **Text secondary:** `text-gray-600` (`#4B5563`)
- **Text muted:** `text-gray-400` (`#9CA3AF`)
- **Success label:** `text-emerald-600 bg-emerald-50`
- **Danger label:** `text-red-500 bg-red-50`
- **Warning label:** `text-amber-600 bg-amber-50`
- **Border:** `border-gray-200` — clean, visible, not heavy

### Dashboard Radius
- All cards: `rounded-2xl` (16px) — non-negotiable
- Large / pastel feature cards: `rounded-[20px]`
- Buttons & inputs: `rounded-xl`
- Tags / pills / badges: `rounded-full`

### Dashboard Shadow
- Cards: `shadow-[0_1px_4px_rgba(0,0,0,0.06),0_4px_16px_rgba(0,0,0,0.04)]`
- Elevated (modal/dropdown): `shadow-[0_8px_32px_rgba(0,0,0,0.12),0_2px_8px_rgba(0,0,0,0.06)]`
- NO glow, NO coloured shadows, NO neon

### Dashboard Layout
- **Top nav only** (h-16, bg-white, border-b border-gray-100) — NO sidebar
- Content area: `bg-[#F0F4FF] p-8`
- KPI grid: `grid grid-cols-4 gap-6`
- Charts/table row: `grid grid-cols-3 gap-6`

### Dashboard Rules
1. NEVER use dark backgrounds (`#0F1117`, `#1C1F2E`, etc.) — that spec is replaced
2. NEVER use Lora in the dashboard — Inter only
3. Mint `#2ECC88` is the primary action/success color (NOT blue)
4. Blue `#4361EE` is for data/nav/links (NOT as primary button color)
5. All cards are white on `#F0F4FF` background
6. KPI numbers are `font-extrabold` (weight 800), never less
7. Use pastel card backgrounds (mint, lavender, sky, yellow) for feature tiles — not plain white
8. Empty states use illustration style: black outlines + mint fill, cream bg `#F5F0E8`
